<p>###<strong>**CONTINUOUS INTEGRATION**</strong></p>

<p>This is something that I still plan on getting better during this quarantine time. I think Iâ€™m able to make things work way better with gitlab, docker and our production servers. If you donâ€™t know what Iâ€™m talking about you can read more about it <a href="https://about.gitlab.com/stages-devops-lifecycle/continuous-integration/">here</a>.</p>

